channel.title: Dom Irrera Live from the Laugh Factory
channel.itunes:summary: Stand up vet Dom Irrera chats up old and new comedian friends live on the world famous Laugh Factory stage with club owner Jamie Masada. Watch these comedy pals recount wild Hollywood tales, discuss their own lives, and consider the comedy business as it is and was, and what it will be.

item.title: Amanda Seales
item.description: Amanda Seales stops by to chat with Dom about getting her start in comedy in New York, adjusting to life in LA, black culture and history, Trump, Bill Cosby, Colin Kaepernick, the Ezekiel Elliot story, male comics telling her what not to say on stage and much more! Plus, Amanda and Dom debate about using the "N-word".
